Escort (5)
- During the day, may choose one player. The following night, all actions performed on the player will be redirected onto themselves.
- They cannot change their target during the night.
- Also may not choose to redirect on the same player twice consecutively, unless they die and respawn.
- Redirection ability will occur throughout the night. 
- Only abilities (both Immediate and End Phase abilities) on their target will be redirected to the Escort.
- Items used on the Escort's target will not be affected.
- Action is used during the day, and is activated on End Phase during the following night.
- Respawns in 4 phases.
